<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>New Login Notification</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { width: 90%; max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; padding: 20px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 5px; }
        .header { font-size: 24px; color: #444; margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .content p { margin-bottom: 10px; }
        .details { background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 20px; }
        .details strong { display: inline-block; width: 120px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; font-size: 0.9em; color: #777; }
        .button { display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; margin-top: 15px; background-color: #007bff; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; }
        .button-danger { background-color: #dc3545; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">New Login to Your Account</div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Hello {{username}},</p>
            <p>We detected a new login to your {{appName}} account. If this was you, you can safely ignore this email. If you do not recognize this login, please secure your account immediately.</p>
            
            <div class="details">
                <p><strong>Date & Time:</strong> {{loginTime}}</p>
                <p><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ipAddress}}</p>
                <p><strong>Approx. Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>
                <p><strong>Browser:</strong> {{browserName}} {{browserVersion}}</p>
                <p><strong>Operating System:</strong> {{osName}} {{osVersion}}</p>
            </div>

            <p>If you don't recognize this activity, please take this step:</p>
            <ol>
                <li><a href="{{resetPasswordLink}}" class="button button-danger">Reset Your Password</a></li>
                <!-- Add link to review active sessions if you implement that feature -->
            </ol>
            
            <p>If this was you, no action is needed. Your account is secure.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            Thanks,<br>
            The {{appName}} Team
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 